libs.content:
find_library(libnoise_libraries
  names libnoise noise libnoiseutils noiseutils
  paths
    $env{libnoise_dir}
    no_default_path
    path_suffixes lib64 lib so
)

find_library(libnoise_libraries
  names libnoise noise libnoiseutils noiseutils
  paths
    ${cmake_source_dir}/lib
    ~/library/frameworks
    /library/frameworks
    /usr/local
    /usr
    /sw
    /opt/local
    /opt/csw
    /opt
    /usr/freeware    
  path_suffixes lib64 lib so
)
